# Fairtrail CLI — Query List
Output packages/cli/demo/fairtrail-list.gif
Output packages/cli/demo/fairtrail-list.mp4

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontFamily "JetBrains Mono"
Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1400
Set Height 600
Set Padding 24
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set PlaybackSpeed 1
Set CursorBlink false

Type "./packages/cli/demo/ft --list"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 5s

Type "q"
Sleep 1s
